snippet: Japanese telecom and media group SoftBank Corp has set its sights on the wireless assets put up for sale by America Movil, the Wall Street Journal reported, citing people familiar with the matter....

headline.print_headline: Japan's SoftBank Sets Sights on America Movil Assets: WSJ
headline.main: Japan's SoftBank Sets Sights on America Movil Assets: WSJ

lead_paragraph: Japanese telecom and media group SoftBank Corp has set its sights on the wireless assets put up for sale by America Movil, the Wall Street Journal reported, citing people familiar with the matter.
